modules.description: Handles sending notifications to GitLab merge requests using configuration values. Works with GitLab API endpoints, project IDs, and merge request details. Useful for CI/CD pipelines reporting build status directly on merge requests.

Handles sending notifications to GitLab merge requests using configuration values. Works with GitLab API endpoints, project IDs, and merge request details. Useful for CI/CD pipelines reporting build status directly on merge requests.

Implements monadic chaining for Lwt_result values and provides a Notifier module for sending GitLab merge request notifications. Handles interactions with GitLab API endpoints, project IDs, and merge request details. Used in CI/CD pipelines to report build statuses directly on GitLab merge requests.
